These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, gospel, blues, d&b
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, lily, orchid, marigold
1. the fan of blues is between the person who growsorchid and the person who growslily##2
2. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
3. the person who growsorchid is not to the left of the person who growsorchid##8
4. the person who growslily is not the fan of blues##6
5. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the fan of folk##5
6. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | folk | blues | gospel  |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | orchid   | marigold  | lily |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, house, r&b, blues
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, water-polo, parkour, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##8
2. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
3. the fan of pop is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the fan of blues is between the fan of pop and the fan of house##2
5. the fan of house is somewhere between the fan of r&b and the person who's sport is snowboarding##7
6. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the fan of house##5
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | house          | blues | pop     |
| Sport    | parkour      | tennis | snowboarding | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, turquise, yellow, pink
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rat, cat, lizard
1. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the left of the person who likes yellow##8
2. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
4. the person who likes turquise is in an even position##4
5. the person who likes pink is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
7. the person who likes pink is the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Color           | light-blue | turquise | yellow     | pink |
| Pet   | rat    | lizard   | chinchilla | cat    |

