.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
City: hamburg, colone, rome, miami
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, bongani, bluemaster, baccarat
1. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the siglo-smoker is not to the left of the bongani-smoker##8
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
4. the person traveling to miami is not to the right of the bluemaster-smoker##8
5. the person traveling to hamburg is the siglo-smoker##1
6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
7. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to miami##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| City   | rome   | colone         | miami   | hamburg    |
| Cigar         | bongani | baccarat | bluemaster | siglo |

