.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, water, fanta, hot-chocolate
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, bike, motorbike, car
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking water##7
2. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking sprite##7
4. the person drinking fanta is not to the left of the person driving the car##8
5. the person driving the car is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person driving the bike##7
6. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
7. the person driving the bike is not to the left of the person drinking sprite##8
8. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | water   | fanta | hot-chocolate | sprite    |
| Transport         | subway | car   | motorbike   | bike |

