4. the futuristic house is somewhere to the right of the chaman-smoker##5
5. the dannemann-smoker is the dannemann-smoker##1
6. the craftsman house is not the tiparillo-smoker##6
7. the ranch-style house is not to the right of the craftsman house##8
8. the chaman-smoker is not to the left of the dannemann-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| House   | ranch-style   | townhouse | craftsman | futuristic |
| Cigar     | baccarat | dannemann       | chaman  | tiparillo    |

