2. the canadian is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
4. the indian is between the canadian and the person watching romance movies##2
5. the egyptian is on the far left##1
6. the person watching action movies is between the person watching musical movies and the person watching western movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
