.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, van, train, tram
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, firefighter, manager, teacher
 1. the teacher is somewhere to the left of the manager##5
 2. the person driving the tram is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
 3. the person driving the bus is the manager##1
 4. the manager is not to the right of the firefighter##8
 5. the teacher is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 6. the firefighter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
 7. the firefighter is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the manager##8
 9. the firefighter is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
10. the person driving the van is not to the left of the pilot##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Transport          | van    | train | bus | tram |
| Job   | pilot | teacher  | manager     | firefighter    |

