.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, cycling, rowing, weightlifting
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, rock, funk, soul
1. the person who's sport is rowing is the fan of r&b##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the left of the fan of rock##8
3. the fan of rock is the fan of rock##1
4. the fan of soul is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person who's sport is cycling is between the fan of rock and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
7. the person who's sport is rowing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Sport    | weightlifting        | cycling | parkour | rowing |
| Music-Genre   | soul | funk | rock   | r&b    |

