.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, crime, superhero, romance
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, rock-climbing, board-games, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the person watching thriller movies##6
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person watching romance movies is not to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
4. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
5. the person watching romance movies is somewhere between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is video-games##7
6. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person watching superhero movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre         | crime    | romance | thriller | superhero |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | hiking      | board-games     | video-games     |

 